Class ProtocolHandler

java.lang.Object
com.inFlight.server.socket.ProtocolHandler
public class ProtocolHandler extends Object
ProtocolHandler is a class that handles incoming messages and performs actions based on the action type. It uses the corresponding services to process requests and return responses.
